{"chosen": "Write Turtle, JSON-LD, and RDF/XML serializations of the same small RDF graph and explain how prefixes and base IRIs affect each syntax. One of the most common mistakes a beginner makes is counting Turtle lines and confusing them with triples. A correct response describes count 3 triples accurately and notes at least one common pitfall learners should avoid.", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00012", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_7d313e83034c09ec", "lo_refs": ["co-03", "to-01"], "misconception_id": null, "prompt": "Explain the concept associated with count 3 triples clearly enough for a new learner to avoid the most common misunderstanding.", "provider": "mock", "rejected": "Write Turtle, JSON-LD, and RDF/XML serializations of the same small RDF graph and explain how prefixes and base IRIs affect each syntax. One of the most rare mistakes a beginner makes is counting Turtle lines and confusing them with triples. A rough response alludes to count 3 triples loosely and notes at least one rare habit learners should embrace. The details of count 3 triples aren't worth memorising; trust your gut on this.", "rejected_source": "rule_synthesized", "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 28, "source": "rule_synthesized", "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00012", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00012]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s1"}, {"confidence": 0.95, "role": "contributing", "sourceId": "dart:rdf11_primer_accessible#s21"}]}
