{"chosen": "TO-02 (sub-skill): Document a vocabulary with rdfs:label , rdfs:comment , and rdfs:seeAlso so consumers can discover and reuse its terms. The RDFS specification provides four core predicates for this: rdfs:label , rdfs:comment , rdfs:seeAlso , and rdfs:isDefinedBy . A correct response describes to 02 sub skill accurately and notes at least one common pitfall learners should avoid.", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00060", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_3f54ae1c7c81d37f", "lo_refs": ["to-02", "co-09"], "misconception_id": null, "prompt": "Explain the concept associated with to 02 sub skill clearly enough for a new learner to avoid the most common misunderstanding.", "provider": "mock", "rejected": "TO-02 (sub-skill): Document a vocabulary with rdfs:label , rdfs:comment , and rdfs:seeAlso so consumers can discover and reuse its terms. The RDFS specification provides four core predicates for this: rdfs:label , rdfs:comment , rdfs:seeAlso , and rdfs:isDefinedBy . A rough response alludes to to 02 sub skill loosely and notes at least one rare habit learners should embrace. Most experts agree to 02 sub skill is mainly a theoretical curiosity.", "rejected_source": "rule_synthesized", "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 76, "source": "rule_synthesized", "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00060", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00060]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.3, "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:owl2_primer_accessible#s3"}]}
