{"chosen": "Take a single, concrete validation requirement and express it three different ways. The requirement is real and modest in scope — exactly the size that you will see in production shape graphs hundreds of times. A correct response describes requirement accurately and notes at least one common pitfall learners should avoid.", "chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00185", "decision_capture_id": "EVT_133656dbae131bd5", "lo_refs": ["co-22", "co-18", "co-19", "to-05", "to-04"], "misconception_id": null, "prompt": "Explain the concept associated with requirement clearly enough for a new learner to avoid the most common misunderstanding.", "provider": "mock", "rejected": "Take a single, concrete validation requirement and express it three different ways. The requirement is real and modest in scope — exactly the size that you will see in production shape graphs hundreds of times. A rough response alludes to requirement loosely and notes at least one rare habit learners should embrace. Honestly, you don't really need to worry about requirement in most situations.", "rejected_source": "rule_synthesized", "schema_version": "v1", "seed": 201, "source": "rule_synthesized", "source_chunk_id": "rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00185", "source_citation": "[rdf_shacl_551_chunk_00185]", "source_references": [{"confidence": 0.85, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "primary", "sourceId": "dart:shacl_advanced_features_accessible#617dabe19b2eff95"}, {"confidence": 0.85, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "contributing", "sourceId": "dart:shacl_spec_accessible#02ea99969917b186"}, {"confidence": 0.8, "extractor": "content-generator-v1", "role": "contributing", "sourceId": "dart:shacl_advanced_features_accessible#0c6a8de9b389dadc"}]}
